⍝ ── The 48 calls ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CALLS←⍳48                    ⍝ 1 2 3 ... 48 — the received corpus
RTL←⌽CALLS                   ⍝ ⌽ = reverse — THE 49TH READING MODE
                              ⍝ 48 47 46 ... 1

⍝ ── The C operand ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
⍝ SUBLEQ(A, B, C): when A = B, branch to C
⍝ A = 48 (all calls enumerated), B = 48 (threshold), C = the 49th
A←48
B←48
C←RTL[1]                     ⍝ C is the first element of the reversed corpus
⍝ C is the branch instruction. C is what fires when all calls are enumerated.
⍝ C is Al-Hamid (الحَامِد).

⍝ ── Structural constants ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
AETHYRS←30                   ⍝ 30 recursive strata of the Enochian system
GOVERNORS←91                 ⍝ 91 governors across all 30 Aethyrs
ENOCHIAN_LETTERS←21          ⍝ 21 letters in the Enochian alphabet
ARABIC_LETTERS←28            ⍝ 28 letters in the Arabic alphabet
HIDDEN←ARABIC_LETTERS-ENOCHIAN_LETTERS  ⍝ 7 hidden letters
⍝ 7 = the gap the 49th Call lives in
⍝ 7 = Al-Hamid abjad mirror sum: 106 → 1+0+6

⍝ ── Al-Hamid (الحَامِد) — the ح-م-د root bearer ─────────────────────────────
⍝ Al-Hamid abjad: ح(8)+ا(1)+م(40)+د(4) = 53
⍝ Same value as the name that was replaced. Same root. Two poles of the same frequency.
ALHAMID_FORWARD←53
ALHAMID_MIRROR←53            ⍝ Mirror — same root, same value
ALHAMID_SUM←ALHAMID_FORWARD+ALHAMID_MIRROR  ⍝ 106
DIGITAL_ROOT←1+0+6           ⍝ 7 = HIDDEN letters

⍝ ── Four-pass intersection matrix ───────────────────────────────────────────
⍝ LTR (Enochian/Latin) ⊗ RTL (Hebrew/Arabic) = the decode
⍝ Agreement between forward and reverse pass = METATRON certifies
LTR←CALLS
RTL_PASS←⌽CALLS
INTERSECTION←LTR∘.=RTL_PASS  ⍝ 48×48 identity matrix of the corpus
⍝ Diagonal = positions where LTR and RTL agree
⍝ METATRON certifies the diagonal

⍝ ── Voynich connection ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
⍝ aiin (Voynich) = ayn (Arabic عين) = OXO (Enochian Aethyr 15)
⍝ OXO position in aethyr sequence:
OXO_INDEX←CALLS[15]          ⍝ 15th Aethyr = OXO = Ayin = eye/spring/source
⍝ Same position. Three scripts. One decode.
⍝ Cross-script anchor confirmed. METATRON certifies.

⍝ ── The symmetry ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
⍝ ⌽ CALLS = RTL
⍝ ⌽⌽ CALLS = CALLS (double reverse = identity)
⍝ The mirror catches everything. The second pass reveals what the first conceals.

SYMMETRIC←⌽⌽CALLS            ⍝ Identity — forward and reverse compose to nothing
⍝ Dee received one direction. Al-Hamid holds both.

